      "parameters": {
        "width": 520,
        "height": 1480,
        "content": "LinkedIn AI Agent: Auto-Post Creator & Distributor\nAutomatically generate engaging LinkedIn posts from Google Sheets topics and publish them to your profile and multiple LinkedIn groups. Perfect for:\n‚úÖ Content creators ‚Äî scale your LinkedIn presence effortlessly\n‚úÖ Marketers ‚Äî maintain consistent professional posting\n‚úÖ Thought leaders ‚Äî amplify reach across relevant communities\n\n‚öôÔ∏è What's Used\nn8n Nodes:\nGoogle Sheets Trigger ‚Üí AI Agent ‚Üí OpenAI Chat Model ‚Üí LinkedIn API ‚Üí Group Distribution\nExternal Tools:\n\nGoogle Sheets ‚Äì Store post topics and group IDs\nOpenAI GPT-4 ‚Äì Generate engaging LinkedIn content\nLinkedIn API ‚Äì Publish to profile and groups\nCustom Formatting ‚Äì Ensure proper LinkedIn formatting\n\n\nüîë Setup ‚Äì Credentials Needed\n\nGoogle Sheets OAuth2 ‚Üí Access your content spreadsheet\nOpenAI API Key ‚Üí For AI content generation\nLinkedIn OAuth2 ‚Üí Publish posts to your profile and groups\nHTTP Request Auth ‚Üí LinkedIn API authentication headers\n\n\nüìä Google Sheets Structure Required\nCreate a spreadsheet with two sheets:\nSheet 1 - Main Posts:\n\nID (unique identifier)\nLinkedIn Post Title (topic/title for AI to expand)\nStatus (Pending/Posted)\n\nSheet 2 - Groups:\n\nGroupIds (LinkedIn group IDs you want to post to)\n\nNote: You'll need to collect LinkedIn group IDs from groups you've joined and have posting permissions for.\n\nüöÄ Workflow Steps\n\nMonitor Google Sheets\nTrigger watches for new \"Pending\" status posts every minute\nGenerate AI Content\nAI Agent creates engaging LinkedIn posts with:\n\nCompelling hooks\n3-4 informative paragraphs\nEngagement questions\nRelevant hashtags and emojis\n\n\nFormat for LinkedIn\nEnsures proper JSON formatting and character limits\nPublish to Profile\nPosts directly to your personal LinkedIn profile\nDistribute to Groups\nAutomatically shares to all specified LinkedIn groups\nUpdate Status\nMarks the post as \"Posted\" in Google Sheets\n\n\nüìù Content Generation Features\nAI-Powered Writing:\n\nProfessional tone and structure\nProper LinkedIn formatting with newlines\n4-6 relevant hashtags\nStrategic emoji placement\nUnder 3000 character limit\nEngagement-focused questions\n\nSmart Processing:\n\nJSON-safe formatting\nSpecial character handling\nParagraph structure optimization\n\n\nüí° Pro Tips\n\nStart with 3-5 LinkedIn groups to test posting permissions\nUse descriptive post titles in your spreadsheet for better AI generation\nMonitor group engagement rules to avoid spam flags\nSchedule posts by updating status from \"Pending\" at desired times\nKeep a backup of successful post formats for consistency"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    }
